Writers:  Paul Levitz
Penciler:  Joe Orlando
Inker:  Larry Mahlstedt
Colorist:  Carl Gafford
Letterer:  John Costanza
Cover:  Steve Lightle and Anthony Tollin

Zymyr takes both Lightning Lass and Lightning Lord to experiment on them, while they both struggle to free themselves. While trapped with her brother Mekt, Lightning Lass reflects upon her life as a Legionnaire. Meanwhile, the Legion of Super-Heroes are recovering from the devastating attack from the Legion of Super-Villains and trying to find their missing teammates. While the missing Legionnaires try to find a way home, Lightning Lass, after escaping Zymyr and defeating her brother, decides to return to the Legion of Super-Heroes.

